    "DisplayTitle": "[Location] needs a bunch of repairs",
    "Description": "Need somebody handy with tools to pop over to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and help out with some repairs. Our last repair guy knocked out most of the fixes but there's still some stuff that could use looking at.\n\nI think if you've got <EM4>six fuses</EM4>, a <EM4>salvaging tool</EM4>, and <EM4>enough RMC canisters to patch up around five pipes</EM4>, you should be covered.\n\nHopefully you know what you're doing, but just in case, the <EM4>\u201cGuide to Maintenance\u201d</EM4> in your mobiGlas Journal might be worth a look.\n\nStows out.",
